m database\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n            \t\t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n\t    \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-23\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2025-12-03\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag revised from publication, adding text and metadata\u003C/change>\n\t\u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\u003Csurface/>\u003C!-- \n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic003618_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic003618.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface> -->\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#JP\" source=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/K7PQWD75\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003Cg ref=\"#cross_greek\">&#x1F7A3;\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>\u003Chi rend=\"supraline\">Κ\u003C/hi>\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ύρι\u003C/ex>\u003Cabbr>\u003Chi rend=\"supraline\">ε\u003C/hi>\u003C/abbr>\u003C/expan> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>\u003Chi rend=\"supraline\">Κ\u003C/hi>\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ύρι\u003C/ex>\u003Cabbr>\u003Chi rend=\"supraline\">ε\u003C/hi>\u003C/abbr>\u003C/expan> μὴ σεν\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">έγκῃς\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>ἰς πιρασμόν ἀλλὰ ῥ\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">ῦσε\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">ἱμᾶς\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>ἀπὸ τοῦ πονιροῦ κὲ\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">τῶν\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">ἀγγέλων\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>τῶν αὐτοῦ ῥῦσε ἱμ\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">ᾶς\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">ἀπ\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\" break=\"no\"/>ὸ τοῦ πονιροῦ κὲ τῶν \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">ἀγγέλ\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"6\" break=\"no\"/>ων αὐτοῦ ῥῦσε ἱμᾶς \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">ἀπὸ\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"7\"/>τῖς ἐπιβουλῖς τῶν ἐπα\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">νιστ\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"8\" break=\"no\"/>αμένων ἱμῖν ὁρατῖς τ\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">οῦ\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"9\"/>ἀοράτου ῥῦσε ἱμᾶς ἀπό συ\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">σ\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"10\" break=\"no\"/>τροφῖς τῶν πονιρευομένων\n                    \u003Clb n=\"11\"/>διασκέδασον τὰς βουλῖς αὐ\n                    \u003Clb n=\"12\" break=\"no\"/>τῶν ἀπὸ ἀνδρὸς ἀδίκου κὲ \u003Csurplus>δ\u003C/surplus>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"13\"/>δίωκε λυδόρου κὲ δυνάσ\n                    \u003Clb n=\"14\" break=\"no\"/>του κὲ συκοφάντου ῥῦσε\n                    \u003Clb n=\"15\"/>τοῦ ὔκου \u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>Συντρό\n                    \u003Clb n=\"16\" break=\"no\"/>φου\u003C/name>\u003C/persName> ἀμίν ἀλλὰ \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">ῥῦσ\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"17\" break=\"no\"/>ε ἱμ\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">ᾶς\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">ἀπὸ\u003C/supplied> \u003Cgap extent=\"unknown\" reason=\"lost\" unit=\"character\"/>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text of Rizzone 2008\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" resp=\"Rizzone\">\n                \u003Cp>Signore, Signore, Signore, non ci indurre in tentazione, ma liberaci dal Maligno e dai suoi angeli, liberaci dal Maligno e dai suoi angeli, liberaci dall'insidia di colore che ci opprimono, (dall'insidia) visibile dell'Invisibile, liberaci dal tumulto dei malvagi, rendi vani i loro disegni, libera dall'uomo iniquo e - caccialo via! - oltraggiatore e prepotente e calunniatore la casa di Syntrophos, ma liberaci (dal Maligno?)...\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>58.1050\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Rizzone\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2008\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>22-26 fig.4\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/K7PQWD75\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001636\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001636\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
